  "combined_text": "--- Main Page ---\nBold Monk | WONDER * ENGAGE * DELIGHT\nMAKE A RESERVATION\nORDER ONLINE FOR PICK-UP\nBOLD MONK HAPPENINGS\nA place\nto simply\nBE\nhome1\nhome2\nhome6\nhome8\nhome3\nhome9\nhome7\nhome11\nLike your favorite piece of music or your most prized work of literature, the Bold Monk exists to bring comfort in your time of leisure. Bold Monk is a place to simply be…to be satisfied, to be joyous, to be connected, to be well.\nTo be yourself.\nIn our\nrestaurant, brewery, bookstore, coffee house, and beer garden\n, you\n’\nll find your space.\nAll online casinos we list will also offer free spins and bonuses to their loyal players, as well as a top-notch live casino with pretty dealers. Bank transfers and direct cash deposits are the best methods to transfer Indian Rupees in your UPI account. To transfer money, register with UPI first and choose a prepaid card within the denomination range of 25 to 500 USD.\nCasino slot machines are a mega hit at any UPI casino India\nhttps://bestindiancasinos.co.in/online-casinos/upi/\n. These wonderful and downright thrilling games are based on reels and adorned with features that make your wins grow exponentially faster. Any casino that is worth considering will have at least 1,000 of these listed in its gallery. A notable feature of this UPI casino is the fantastic categorization of games that Bons is offering where a heap of filtering options are available.\nMONDAY – THURSDAY\n: 11:30am – 10pm\nFRIDAY:\n11:30am – 11pm\nSATURDAY:\n10:30am – 11pm\nSUNDAY:\n10:30am – 10pm\nBrunch Service Ends at 3pm on Saturday + Sunday\nMAKE A RESERVATION\nPhone 404-390-3288\nWe’re located at\nTHE COMPLEX\n1737 ELLSWORTH INDUSTRIAL\nBLVD NW BLDG D\nATLANTA, GA 30318\nDIRECTIONS\nLUNCH + DINNER\n|\nB\nRUNCH\nBEER + WINE + COCKTAIL\nEAT\nSustainable, wholesome cuisine that blur the lines between\nBELGIAN FARE\n,\nSOUTHERN COMFORT\n, and\nCALIFORNIA FRESH\n. Offering breakfast, lunch, and dinner daily with brunch served on weekends.\nSEE MENU\nBREW\nConnecting the hearts of humanity to the benevolence of our earth through the simple, ancient ingredients and intensive, devoted craftsmanship of our\nBELGIAN-INSPIRED BEERS\n. Enjoy beers brewed in-house and served fresh from the cask, as well as many other local and global beers.\nSEE MENU\nDRINK\nA highly-curated consumption experience boasting a producer-based\nWINE\nlist, an evolving roster of inventive craft\nCOCKTAILS\n, and an artisan\nCOFFEE\nprogram featuring proprietary blends from Methodical Coffee.\nSEE MENU\nHOST\nA warm blend of natural materials creates flexible dining and\nENTERTAINING SPACES\nwith a range of hosting capabilities from intimate meetings to large, festive receptions. Contact us for help with your event.\nSEE GROUP SPACES\nOur\nDearly\nBeloved.\n\n--- Page: /menus ---\nMenus | Bold Monk\nFOOD AND BEVERAGE\nPurposely designed to promote harmony and a shared spirit of joy.\nMAKE A RESERVATION\nORDER ONLINE FOR PICK-UP\nLUNCH + DINNER\n|\nB\nRUNCH\nBEER + WINE + COCKTAIL\nWe’ve taken every effort to create an enjoyable dining environment and continue to be conscious of social distancing as we return to regular beverage and dining service. If you have specific needs, please let our team know.\nAt Bold Monk, we offer a variety of experiences, including a bookstore with curated selections for purchase in our upstairs Abbey, Bold Monk retail gifts located at our host area, and a beer garden located across the bridge from the Abbey upstairs.\nThanks for joining us!\n“Passion is universal humanity. Without it religion, history, romance and art would be useless.”\n-Honore de Balzac\nOur\nDearly\nBeloved.\n\n--- Page: /wp-content/uploads/2025/11/BMB-Dining-Room-menu-112525.pdf ---\n%PDF-1.7\n4 0 obj\n(Identity)\nendobj\n5 0 obj\n(Adobe)\nendobj\n8 0 obj\n<<\n/Filter /FlateDecode\n/Length 123775\n/Length1 282708\n/Type /Stream\n>>\nstream\nx��\t\\[ǵ0>s��.��]B,Z�\u0004\b\u0010Bl\u0002\u0001\u0017\u0010\u0018�\u0017��\r�